txt.en: The spiders of the Snares in Kingsfell have covered this little valley in sticky webs, creating a dangerous potential trap for any unlucky enough to stumble into this place. It would be unwise to linger here any longer than necessary.\n\nYou should defeat a number of spiders as quickly as you can.
You have swiftly defeated a number of the Kingsfell spiders in the Snares, helping to make the area near Esteldín safer and free of the influence of evil.
